text: Christine Wolf (born 5 March 1989) is an Austrian professional golfer. Wolf is a graduate of the University of Tennessee at Chattanooga. Wolf turned professional in 2012 and played on the LET Access Series from 2012 to 2013, winning one event. She has played on the Ladies European Tour since 2014. In 2015, Wolf finished runner-up to Holly Clyburn at the NSW Women's Open, an ALPG Tour event.
